rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0001
rows.name:
These strange boxes... I've seen things
like them before from time to time,
when I was salvaging.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I always thought they were some kind
of houses, but what would houses be
doing on roads?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0003
rows.name: Looks like there's no way through...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0005
rows.name: I wonder what's past here...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's the highest point of all Alst,
but there's so much space...
It's kinda unbelievable.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0101
rows.name:
These weird boxes... They pop up all
over the place in Eden.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0102
rows.name: What the heck were they for, though?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0103
rows.name: No way past, it seems...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0104
rows.name:
Such a massive space...
How did people get around it...?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0201
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh!
This made out of steel?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0202
rows.name:
No...seems a bit stronger than steel,
and lighter too! Very intriguing!

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0203
rows.name:
Bunch of rubble?
It no match for Hana's power!

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0204
rows.name:
...Ah, no, Tora take it back.
Please pay no mind to Tora.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0205
rows.name:
Tora realize, only thing we find
behind rubble is more rubble...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0301
rows.name:
These boxes are quite unfamiliar, but
something about them reminds me of
the imperial weapon called Cetus.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0302
rows.name:
Perhaps they are some manner
of vehicle?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0303
rows.name:
To make such a great gaping hole in
the rock wall... Incredible...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0304
rows.name:
The technology here gives one pause...
But it was still no match for the power
of time passing.

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0401
rows.name:
Hey, these things aren't going to
start moving or anything, right?

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0402
rows.name:
They look kind of like those weird
machines we saw in Mors and
the World Tree...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0403
rows.name:
The construction of this wall reminds
me of the sturdy walls of Teos Aure...

rows.label: tlk00000595_01_msg0404
rows.name:
But even beyond it, I'm sure nothing is
waiting other than more rubble-strewn
desolation, same as here...
